; Regression test for issue #2872
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/2872
;
; The original test for issue #1948 used "format 1000.000 CTG25" where
; CTG25 was intended as a mismatching commodity symbol. However, unquoted
; commodity names cannot contain digits (they terminate the symbol), so
; "CTG25" is silently parsed as "CTG". The 1948.test was updated to use
; "CTGBAR" to avoid this ambiguity.
;
; This file tests:
; 1. That a quoted commodity name with digits ("CTG25") works correctly in
;    a format directive when it matches the commodity name.
; 2. That a mismatched quoted commodity name with digits produces a clear,
;    accurate error message (naming the full symbol, including digits).

; Valid: commodity "CTG25" with format using "CTG25" should succeed
commodity "CTG25"
    format 1000.000 "CTG25"

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses        1000.000 "CTG25"
    Assets

test source -> 0
end test
